			<td>You can also make text __bold__ or *italic*.</td>
			<td>You can also make text <strong>bold</strong> or <em>italic</em>.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>Here's an image: ![Turtl logo](https://turtl.it/images/favicon.png)</td>
